{"tid":2090793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一post叫和你eat放d code比下手搞好嘛？","createTime":"2020-07-02T10:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T09:07:41.000Z","uid":76845,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"70a01d8e8d5311a89c9c8e934b138df370f296b8","tid":2090793,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"和你eat是個好東西 去平時唔會去嘅地方全靠佢搵藍店<br />\n縮唔緊要 希望佢可以放個database出嚟比信得過人搞<br />\n等大家知道邊到搵藍店幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebf1dfa9fc1267116b6541753e7038371fc5c27","tid":2090793,"uid":293635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"我仍然好需要呢個app！！請你再黎推介過啦！！<br />\n<br />\n做人咁辛苦，食到滿足一餐先順氣啲，呢大半年搵食完全靠你推介，搵到好多正的食店，不如你繼續用個人推介的形式列出食店啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如用sharp醒暖色系例如黃紅橙列出你覺得你會再食的舖頭，同埋用啲冷色系例如藍紫綠去列出啲你覺得未必再食的舖頭啦！就算唔講原因都得！！信得過你！！<br />\n<br />\n呢大半年和你搵食，我很愉快！！我好需要你繼續推介搵好西食！！繼續推介好嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd6593d8786dadffcc16146096da852704cfabf","tid":2090793,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc290e2ac4d325f7ff9e3d4245ad0781e9deb053","tid":2090793,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"08150ef17bcb39624befb4f9ace79b75a5b8049b","tid":2090793,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"pish ahhh"},{"pid":"f8d58067c0cc5d310c65ea5fa53234ae63bb9c4d","tid":2090793,"uid":13549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T04:24:57.000Z","msg":"唔放黃店 最起